/// @file BattleUi.prefab
/// <summary>
/// Prefab of %Battle's UI.
/// </summary>
///
/// BattleUi-prefab holds all %Battle's %UI GameObjects.
///
/// ### Structure
/// - **BattleUi**  
///   All @uihandlerslink are attached to this GameObject and @dirref{Altzone,Assets/Altzone/Resources/Prefabs/BattleUiShared} -prefabs are instantiated as children.
///     - *Components:*
///         - RectTransform
///         - @cref{Battle.View.UI,BattleUiController}
///         - @cref{Battle.View.UI,BattleUiAnnouncementHandler}
///         - @cref{Battle.View.UI,BattleUiGameOverHandler}
///         - @cref{Battle.View.UI,BattleUiTimerHandler}
///         - @cref{Battle.View.UI,BattleUiDiamondsHandler}
///         - @cref{Battle.View.UI,BattleUiGiveUpButtonHandler}
///         - @cref{Battle.View.UI,BattleUiPlayerInfoHandler}
///         - @cref{Battle.View.UI,BattleUiJoystickHandler}
///         - @cref{Battle.View.UI,BattleUiDebugStatsOverlayHandler}
///         - Canvas
///         - CanvasScaler
///         - GraphicRaycaster
///     - *Children:*
///         - **BattleUiTimer** (@ref BattleUiTimer.prefab)  
///           Displays game timer.
///         - **AnnouncementText**  
///           Displays on-screen notifications such as the countdown.
///             - *Components:*
///                 - RectTransform
///                 - @cref{Altzone.Scripts.BattleUiShared,TextScaler}
///                 - CanvasRenderer
///                 - TextMeshPro - Text (UI)
///                 - WorkSans-Regular SDF Material (Material)
///         - **BattleUiPlayerInfo1** (@ref BattleUiPlayerInfo.prefab)  
///           Displays local player's player info.
///         - **BattleUiPlayerInfo2** (@ref BattleUiPlayerInfo.prefab)  
///           Displays teammate's player info.
///         - **GameOverView**  
///           End of game popup which has button to exit game.
///             - *Components:*
///                 - RectTransform
///             - *Children:*
///                 - **background**
///                     - *Components:*
///                         - Image
///                 - **TitleText**
///                     - *Components:*
///                         - TextMeshPro - Text (UI)
///                 - **GoalByText**
///                     - *Components:*
///                         - TextMeshPro - Text (UI)
///                 - **RestartButton**
///                     - *Components:*
///                         - Image
///                         - Button
///                     - *Children:*
///                         - **Text (TMP)**
///                             - *Components:*
///                                 - RectTransform
///                                 - CanvasRenderer
///                                 - TextMeshPro - Text (UI)
///                 - **ExitGameButton**
///                     - *Components:*
///                         - Image
///                         - Button
///                     - *Children:*
///                         - **Text (TMP)**
///                             - *Components:*
///                                 - RectTransform
///                                 - CanvasRenderer
///                                 - TextMeshPro - Text (UI)
///                 - *Shared components:*
///                     - RectTransform
///                     - CanvasRenderer
///         - **DebugStatsOverlay**  
///           Debug overlay for displaying currently selected character's stats.
///             - *Components:*
///                 - RectTransform
///             - *Children:*
///                 - **ImpactForceHolder**
///                 - **HpHolder**
///                 - **SpeedHolder**
///                 - **CharSizeHolder**
///                 - **DefenceHolder**
///                 - *Shared components:*
///                     - RectTransform
///                 - *Shared children:*
///                     - **StatName**
///                     - **StatValue**
///                     - *Shared components:*
///                         - RectTransform
///                         - CanvasRenderer
///                         - TextMeshPro - Text (UI)
///         - **BattleUiDiamonds** (@ref BattleUiDiamonds.prefab)  
///           Display's diamonds collected during the match.
///         - **BattleUiGiveUpButton** (@ref BattleUiGiveUpButton.prefab)  
///           Button for giving up the game.
///         - **BattleUiJoystick1** (@ref BattleUiJoystick.prefab)  
///           Movement on-screen joystick.
///         - **BattleUiJoystick2** (@ref BattleUiJoystick.prefab)  
///           Rotation on-screen joystick.